  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/63848ad76993add07b8c4f70bffc9ccc.poster.avif?t=1771945070\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/63848ad76993add07b8c4f70bffc9ccc.webm?t=1771945070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Mamma mia! Our cats are now in the great city of Rome! Let's search for them.<br><strong>A short and pleasant experience in a big and lovely illustration!</strong> Start with a Beautiful monochromatic scenario, relax, and find all the cats to reveal the final colored art.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/abb2dcc3e3b4851e9dec701f8103d3fc.webp?t=1771945070\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>More than 970 hidden objects!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/abb2dcc3e3b4851e9dec701f8103d3fc.webp?t=1771945070\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>Play through different modes, find special cats, and unlock bonus levels!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/0e4ab7d837589c3af13dc9bad2fbaba7.avif?t=1771945070\" width=616 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NORMAL MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 120 cats in fixed positions.<br></li><li>3 hints.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADVANCED MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 200 cats in semi-random positions.<br></li><li> 12 Special cats that unlock Bonus Levels and give hints.<br></li><li> 20 city people to find and earn hints.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/832cc51236bc06f898e969f79d1ec71c.poster.avif?t=1771945070\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/832cc51236bc06f898e969f79d1ec71c.webm?t=1771945070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Bonus levels with different sizes and numbers of kittens to find. One use of hint for helping.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Gelateria:</strong> 50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Osteria: </strong>50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Pastificio:</strong> 50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Cat Sanctuary:</strong> 75 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Basilica:</strong> 100 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Fontana:</strong> 100 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Nerd Arena:</strong> 100 kittens + 100 people</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560530/extras/3ede01a44a40eb2fa24357af579df04c.webp?t=1771945070\" width=584 height=41 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark Mode<br></li><li>Invert Mouse Zoom<br></li><li>Mouse Drag Sensibility<br></li><li>Edge Screen Scrolling<br></li><li>Color Blindness</li></ul>",
